subject: Re: JUnit Test Suite With Eclipse 3.2.0
msgSnippet: I had this problem.  Look at the properties for your project and make sure JDK compliance level is set to 5.0 (click on main Java Compiler property branch).
messageBody:
I had this problem. Look at the properties for your project and make
sure JDK compliance level is set to 5.0 (click on main Java Compiler
property branch).

--- In junit@yahoogroups.com, "leonardobsjr" <leonardobsjr@...> wrote:
> ...when i try to create a
> testSuite, the GUI doesn't recognize any of the annotations.
